## State Management Mapping

| Livewire / Blade | React |
|-----------------|-------|
| `public $name = ''` | `const [name, setName] = useState('')` |
| `public array $items = []` | `const [items, setItems] = useState([])` |
| `mount()` data load | `useEffect(() => { fetch... }, [])` |
| `updatedName()` hook | `useEffect(() => { ... }, [name])` |
| `#[Computed]` property | `useMemo(() => ..., [deps])` |
| `wire:model="name"` | `value={name} onChange={e => setName(e.target.value)}` |
| `wire:click="save"` | `onClick={save}` |
| `wire:submit="submit"` | `onSubmit={handleSubmit}` |

