## Common Blade → JSX Patterns

### Conditional Rendering

**Blade:**

```blade
@if($isLoggedIn)
    <p>Welcome, {{ $user->name }}</p>
@else
    <a href="/login">Login</a>
@endif
```

**React:**

```tsx
{isLoggedIn ? <p>Welcome, {user.name}</p> : <a href="/login">Login</a>}
// or
{isLoggedIn && <p>Welcome, {user.name}</p>}
```

### Loops

**Blade:**

```blade
@foreach($products as $product)
    <div>{{ $product['name'] }}</div>
@endforeach
```

**React:**

```tsx
{products.map(product => (
    <div key={product.id}>{product.name}</div>
))}
```

### Slots / Layout

**Blade layout:**

```blade
<x-layouts.app>
    <x-slot:header><h1>Products</h1></x-slot:header>
    <p>Content</p>
</x-layouts.app>
```

**React layout (Outlet):**

```tsx
// components/AppLayout.tsx
import { Outlet } from 'react-router-dom';

export default function AppLayout() {
    return (
        <div>
            <nav>Navbar</nav>
            <main><Outlet /></main>
        </div>
    );
}
```

